author: Megan Peters
title: 5 Best Cartoon Network Series Of The 90s
text:
5 Best Cartoon Network Series Of The 90s Megan Peters Start Slideshow Slide of 
Whether you’re a 90s kid or not, it’s hard not to love cartoons born from the era. Thanks to networks like Cartoon Network and Nickelodeon, a flood of animated treasures made their debut prior to the new millennia, and many of the shows remain evergreen today. 
Here at ComicBook.com, we took it upon ourselves to do the hard task of narrowing down five of Cartoon Network’s best series from the 90s. So, go buy from Fruit By The Foot and slip on your old Jellies. It’s time we dove into the nostalgic world of Cartoon Network’s finest shows. (Photo: Cartoon Network )
